content.rendered:
We’re thrilled to announce the establishment of the Kosovo Business Angels Network! 

 

Mark your calendar for April 15-17, 2024, as we embark on this incredible journey of fostering entrepreneurship and innovation in Kosova!. Join us as we bring together aspiring entrepreneurs and seasoned investors to create a vibrant ecosystem that nurtures groundbreaking ideas and drives economic growth. Whether you’re a visionary entrepreneur with a game-changing concept or a seasoned investor seeking promising opportunities, KOSOVA BUSINESS ANGELS NETWORK is your gateway to success!

 

Stay tuned for more details on our inaugural event and how you can be a part of this monumental initiative!
